data.title: Animal Crossing: New Horizons: everything you need to know about the Nintendo Switch adventure
data.meta_description: Animal Crossing: New Horizons for the Nintendo Switch is the latest entry in Nintendos long-running life-simulation series, following titles like New Leaf and Pocket Camp.
data.text:
Animal Crossing is one of Nintendos most unassuming series. Its quaint and relaxing, with no clear-cut goals, and it doesnt feature the companys most iconic characters like Mario or Link. But it has also become one of Nintendos biggest franchises, growing from a Japan-only release on the N64 to a tentpole title gracing most Nintendo platforms and even expanding to smartphones. New Horizons for the Switch is the biggest entry to date, one that promises to expand with regular, seasonal updates. You can keep track of everything you need to know about the game with the stories below.
